    "created_at": "2016-05-14T17:42:24Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-14T17:42:24Z",
    "body": "Even better, we don't have to patch Chromium to do this:\n1. [MachBroker::GetMachPortName](https://code.google.com/p/chromium/codesearch#chromium/src/content/browser/mach_broker_mac.mm&q=rohitfork&sq=package:chromium&type=cs&l=95) calls \n2. [base::MachPortBroker::GetMachPortName](https://code.google.com/p/chromium/codesearch#chromium/src/base/mac/mach_port_broker.h&q=GetMachPort&sq=package:chromium&type=cs&l=48), which is configured by\n3. [base::BaseBundleID](https://code.google.com/p/chromium/codesearch#chromium/src/base/mac/foundation_util.h&q=BaseBundleID&sq=package:chromium&type=cs&l=172) which can just be get/set\n"
  },
